# ❌ Error: PR/PO Integration Failure

## 🧩 Problem
PR or PO not transferring between Ariba and S4.

## 🌍 Scenario
PR created but PO not generated or stuck in integration.

## 🔍 Root Cause
- CIG issues  
- Mapping errors  
- Missing master data  
- Approval incomplete  

## ⚠️ Common Errors
- Document stuck in CIG  
- PO not created  
- Queue failure  

## ✅ Solution
1. Check Ariba document status  
2. Verify approval completion  
3. Check CIG logs  
4. Validate mapping  
5. Reprocess document  

## 🧠 Approach
Break flow → Ariba → CIG → S4  
Find exact failure point.

## 🎯 Learning
Never debug blindly — identify failure stage first.
